{"tid":1311410,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"梁振英呼籲全國人民抵制寶礦力","createTime":"2019-07-13T07:24:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-13T09:02:41.000Z","uid":244242,"like":0,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1e9cc3e1b75a5de73fbf00536aa31e3cc72dab3d","tid":1311410,"uid":244242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T07:24:37.000Z","msg":"前特首、全國政協副主席梁振英昨深夜在Facebook指，「寶礦力黑白不分，我呼籲全國消費者，全面抵制寶礦力。」<br />\n<br />\n環球網昨還引述TVB發言人表示，示威者是在網上「欺凌及恐嚇」TVB廣告客戶，要求他們撤銷投放在TVB的廣告，而寶礦力水特的決定「可能是希望討好示威者」，呼籲該公司「不應也不能對暴力低頭」。報道又指，TVB向該網傳送一份回應，稱對事件「極度遺憾」，強調「任何對無綫電視不恰當的打壓，均不會影響本台公正不偏、客觀持平的新聞報道原則」。<br />\nsource:<a href=\"https://www.am730.com.hk/news/新聞/撤tvb廣告-寶礦力水特致歉-180020\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.am730.com.hk%2Fnews%2F%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%2F%E6%92%A4tvb%E5%BB%A3%E5%91%8A-%E5%AF%B6%E7%A4%A6%E5%8A%9B%E6%B0%B4%E7%89%B9%E8%87%B4%E6%AD%89-180020&d=ev%2BvVaAtQ3cORw7W3wlzWUYD92OErucUe%2F0sHRi%2FZkY%3D&h=124a8164\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.am730.com.hk/news/新聞/撤tvb廣告-寶礦力水特致歉-180020</a>"},{"pid":"57371737ed14ae1dd9a7c4eb430676baaa210026","tid":1311410,"uid":244242,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T07:25:12.000Z","msg":"689想繼續搞亂香港？"},{"pid":"46cd3773e7c789e0c6f07b15a496098f15ea286a","tid":1311410,"uid":244242,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T07:25:48.000Z","msg":"點解會黎左動漫台...<br />\nsor禁錯"},{"pid":"dc94bd24d85635f8e001e4181ae85ba07b47b218","tid":1311410,"uid":244242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T07:53:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e98bef89c5441153297e159f6d5093bf29c55f6c","tid":1311410,"uid":25560,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"46cd3773e7c789e0c6f07b15a496098f15ea286a","tid":1311410,"uid":244242,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T07:25:48.000Z","msg":"點解會黎左動漫台...<br />\nsor禁錯"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T08:05:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/w